	<li id="menu-item-114452" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category"><a href="https://lithub.com/category/lithubradio/the-maris-review/">The Maris Review</a></li>
	<li id="menu-item-113395" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category"><a href="https://lithub.com/category/lithubradio/new-books-network/">New Books Network</a></li>
	<li id="menu-item-199736" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category"><a href="https://lithub.com/category/lithubradio/open-form/">Open Form</a></li>
	<li id="menu-item-113397" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category"><a href="https://lithub.com/category/lithubradio/otherppl-with-brad-listi/">Otherppl with Brad Listi</a></li>
	<li id="menu-item-113396" class="menu-item menu-item-type-taxonomy menu-item-object-category"><a href="https://lithub.com/category/lithubradio/so-many-damn-books/">So Many Damn Books</a></li>
